image_analysis.description: A page from a book or document containing four distinct photographs with accompanying captions. The photos depict various individuals including Leslie Wexner, Jeffrey Epstein, Ghislaine Maxwell, Tony Randall, Deborah Blohm, Gwendolyn Beck, Donald Trump, and Ingrid Seynhaeve in social settings.
image_analysis.layout: The page is organized with four photographs, each paired with a descriptive caption. The layout is a grid-like arrangement with text blocks placed adjacent to their respective images.

Leslie Wexner, photographed
at his home in New York City,
1989 (© Lynn Goldsmith)

(L to R) Jeffrey Epstein, Ghislaine
Maxwell, and Tony Randall, who
presided over a November 1991
YIVO Institute event at the Plaza
Hotel to honor the late Robert
Maxwell (Marina Garnier)

(L to R) Deborah
Blohm, Jeffrey Epstein,
Ghislaine Maxwell, and
Gwendolyn Beck attend a
reception at Mar-a-Lago,
1995. (Davidoff Studios)

Jeffrey Epstein, Donald
Trump, and (newly signed
Trump Model) Ingrid
Seynhaeve, attending the
Victoria's Secret Angels
party at Laura Belle club
in New York City on April
8, 1997 (Marina Garnier)
